1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
Hello.

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:05,500
I am a solo developer, Yeon Sam-Heum.

3
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:08,500
For 17 years, I have been running a company,

4
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:14,000
and with AI, I have created over 200 websites,
600,000 pages.

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,000
This work is not newly created.

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,000
It is a tool that has grown over 8 years — WIA Geulsalim.

7
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
95% of humanity's 5,000 years of knowledge
is still out of reach.

8
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:32,000
87% of Korean historical documents remain
dormant, not yet digitized,

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:40,000
and among the 7,000 languages in the world, 97% have
AI translation and speech quality that are significantly lacking or non-existent.

10
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
300 million people with sensory disabilities
still cannot touch books.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:50,000
These four barriers must be addressed all at once.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,500
Geulsalim operates a four-step pipeline —
restoration, structuring, conversion, delivery.

13
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:59,500
From now on, I will show you through four demos.

14
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,000
The first demo — restoration.

15
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:10,000
The Diffusion model restores damaged historical documents,
and the language model infers the missing characters.

16
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Restoration is not manipulation.

17
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:20,000
The original hash is permanently preserved.

18
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,000
The second demo — structuring.

19
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:36,000
An untagged PDF is automatically structured into WCAG 2.2 compliant HTML,
with AI generating alternative text as well.

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:42,000
On the WIA Book accessibility check site,
I am already automatically checking 80 items.

21
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
The third demo — EPUB accessibility restoration.

22
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:00,000
We automatically restore an accessibility-noncompliant EPUB 2 to EPUB 3.

23
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:06,000
It passes all 80 inspection items.

24
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:13,000
It satisfies four international standards simultaneously:
WCAG, EPUB A11y, KS X 6201, and the European EAA.

25
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:19,000
The fourth demo — multimodal delivery.

26
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Braille in 7,000 languages,
voice in 254 languages,

27
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:29,000
WIA Talk 3D sign language,
436 interactive tools and simulators.

28
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:36,000
WIA Live enables deaf and blind individuals to
communicate directly without an interpreter,

29
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,500
and it is already in pilot operation.

30
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,000
Our Geulsalim.

31
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:46,000
弘益人間 — benefiting all, sustainably.
We're Geulsalim.
